lume come from different intellectual traditions, embracing a multidisciplinary approach combining influences from literary criticism, history, philology, and anthropology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Apr 2019) 0aLiterature, MedievalxHistory and criticism. 0aMonsters in literature. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh1 aBarreiro, Santiago Francisco, eeditor.1 aCordo Russo, Luciana Mabel, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package 2016-2018z978311066731808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press  eBook Package 2018z978311060672040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048535132zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789048535132.jpg  a978-3-11-060672-0  Amsterdam University Press  eBook Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-066731-8  AUP eBook Package 2016-2018  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG